how your element is transform.

(1) rotate => rotate(), rotateX(), rotateY(), rotateZ(), rotate3d()

(2) scale (zooming) => scale(), scaleX(), scaleY(), scaleZ(), scale3d()

(3) skew (streching) => skew(), skewX(), skewY()

(4) translate (movement) => translate(), translateX(), translateY(), translateZ(), translate3d()

(5) perspective (view) => perspective()

(6) matrix => matrix() => 2*3, 
        matrix3d() 4*4

        => https://ramlmn.github.io/visualizing-matrix3d/